-- Nordstrom CFO says to increase debt level
-- 
-- Mon Nov 19, 2007 5:04pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/19/us-nordstrom-debt-idUSN1937540420071119

 

 LOS ANGELES  (Reuters) - Nordstrom Inc. ( JWN.N ) Chief Financial Officer Mike Koppel said on Monday that the upscale department store retailer should increase its debt level somewhat. 

 "We have concluded that Nordstrom should add a moderate amount of leverage," Koppel said on a conference call with analysts to discuss the company's quarterly results. (Reporting by  Nichola Groom )